summary.title: Case Effort Summary
summary.description: Enter or update the estimated effort to complete this Case. This section shows a summary of how much effort the entire Case is estimated to take (Estimated), how much effort has actually been spent on the Case (Actual) and how much effort is estimated to be remaining on the Case (Estimated Remaining).

tooltips.estimated: This is how much effort is estimated to be needed to complete this Case. It is the sum of the ‘Estimated’ effort of all the created and yet-to-be created Actions (and Sub Case Actions) that make up this Case. Note that increasing this value will increase the ‘Work Not Yet Created’ estimate and vice versa.
tooltips.actual: This is how much effort has been spent working on this Case. It is the sum of the ‘Actual’ effort of all the Actions (and Sub Case Actions) that make up this Case, taken from the Time Tracker.
tooltips.remaining: This is how much time is estimated to be left on the Case. It is the sum of the ‘Estimated Remaining’ effort of all the created and yet-to-be created Actions (and Sub Case Actions) that make up this Case.

breakdown.title: Effort Breakdown for Created Work
breakdown.description: Enter or update the estimated effort to complete each of the created Actions (and Sub Cases) that make up this Case. As Actions (and Sub Cases) get created, the estimated effort for them will be taken from the Estimated effort value from the Work Not Yet Created section below.

tooltips.estimated:
This is a breakdown of how much effort each created Action (and Sub Case Action) that makes up this Case is estimated to take. 

Note that changes to any ‘Estimated’ time here will affect the ‘Estimated’ effort for work that is yet-to-be created and might affect the total ‘Estimated’ effort for the Case.
tooltips.actual: This is a breakdown of how much effort has been spent on each created Action (and Sub Case Action) that makes up this Case, taken from their individual time trackers.
tooltips.remaining: This is a breakdown of how much effort is estimated to be left on each created Action (and Sub Case Action) that makes up this Case. It is the difference between the ‘Actual’ effort and the ‘Estimated’ effort.

other.title: Effort for Work Not Yet Created
other.description: Enter or update the estimated effort to complete the Actions (and Sub Cases) that have not yet been created for this Case. As more Actions (and Sub Cases) get created, the estimated effort for them will be subtracted from the Estimated effort value here.
